(1235, 40, 'criteria_column_2', '<h3>HOW REWILDABLE?</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Original habitat intact or restorable?</li>\r\n	<li>Are original causes of the extinction known and correctable?</li>\r\n	<li>Will the species breed easily in captivity?</li>\r\n	<li>Are its skills for the wild independent of wild-parent training?</li>\r\n	<li>Is rewilding workable for the species?</li>\r\n	<li>Is rewilding the species workable for the habitat?</li>\r\n</ul>'),
