(1351, 370, 'ted-ex-box-home', '<img class="alignright" style="width: 270px;" alt="" src="http://rare.longnow.org/Resources/tedxlive.jpeg" width="281" height="208" />\r\n<h2 class="larger">Convening meetings and workshops of de-extinction pioneers</h2>\r\n<ul class="bottom">\r\n	<li>Convened an exploratory meeting at Harvard in February 2012 on reviving the passenger pigeon. (See report.)</li>\r\n	<li>Organized a private workshop for de-extinction pioneers October 23-24 at National Geographic. (See report.)</li>\r\n	<li>Planning a public conference for de-extinction pioneers and related specialists at National Geographic—TEDx DeExtinction, March 15, 2013. (See meetings.)</li>\r\n</ul>'),
