ies be treated as genetically modified organisms?</dd>\r\n<dd>Should Environmental Impact Reports be required before release?</dd>\r\n<dd>What kind of ecological analysis should be required before release?</dd>\r\n<dd>Is release to the wild irreversible?</dd>\r\n</dl>', 'Ethics', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-3', '', '', '2013-01-17 03:25:31', '2013-01-17 03:25:31', '', 11, 'http://rare.sansink.com/11-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
