o their former native habitat?</dd><dd> </dd><dd>Should revived species be treated as genetically modified organisms?</dd><dd> </dd><dd>Should Environmental Impact Reports be required before release?</dd><dd> </dd><dd>What kind of ecological analysis should be required before release?</dd><dd> </dd><dd>Is release to the wild irreversible?</dd></dl></dd></dl>', 'Ethics', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-2', '', '', '2013-01-17 03:21:41', '2013-01-17 03:21:41', '', 11, 'http://rare.sansink.com/11-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
