ographic‘s historic Hubbard Hall. <strong>Back row</strong>, left to right: Nathan Wolfe, Mary Schweitzer, Robert Lanza, Stanley Temple, Hillary Bok, Henri Kerkdijk-Otten, Frans Vera, Michael Archer, Ben Novak. <strong>4th row</strong>: Kate Jones, Alejandro Camacho, Marilyn Renfree, Joel Berger, Guojie Zhang, Michael McGrew, Andrew French. <strong>3rd row</strong>: Insung Hwang, Jean-Marie Rouillard, Oliver Ryder, Michael Hofreiter, Alberto Fernández, David Burney. <strong>2d row</strong>: William Powell, Jacob Sherkow, Tom Gilbert, Eugene Potapov. <strong>Front row</strong>: Jamie Shreeve, Hank Greely, Hendrik Poinar, Ryan Phelan, Stewart Brand, Ross MacPhee, Sergey Zimov. (Missing from photo: George Church, Peter Kareiva, Terry Garcia, John Francis.)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td height="96"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="f-sp">\r\n<td><img style="float: left;" alt="" src="Resources/_clear.gif" width="25" height="1" border="0" /></td>\r\n<td><img style="float: left;" alt="" src="Resources/_clear.gif" width="955" height="1" border="0" /></td>\r\n<td height="27"><img style="float: left;" alt="" src="Resources/_clear.gif" width="1" height="1" border="0" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table width="1001" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><colgroup> <col width="490" /> <col width="21" /> <col width="3" /> <col width="82" /> <col width="312" /> <col width="92" /> <col width="1" /> </colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td rowspan="6" bgcolor="#ffffff" height="5636">\r\n<table width="490" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><colgroup> <col width="4" /> <col width="482" /> <col width="4" /> </colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign="top">\r\n<td style="background-image: url(''Resources/item4.png'');" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="4" height="4"><img style="float: left;" alt="" src="Resources/_clear.gif" width="1" height="1" border="0" /></td>\r\n<td style="background-image: url(''Resources/item4a.png'');" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="482" height="4"><img style